    "created_at": "2017-06-17T00:30:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-06-17T00:30:26Z",
    "body": "Thanks for the PR, @calmandniceperson. Great handle, too :)\r\n\r\nThe electron-i18n repo doesn't currently include the top-level README or the code of conduct, but maybe it should?\r\n\r\nThe Contributor Covenant already has translations so we should probably just prominently link to http://contributor-covenant.org/i18n/ rather than duplicating the effort."
  },
